deck: Zack Kaplan is a comic book writer debuting his first book, Top Cow and Image Comics new series, ECLIPSE. He taught screenwriting at the International Academy of Film and TV, located in the Philippines. He is a member of the WGA and also writes film and television. He lives in Los Angeles with his wife and daughter.
name: Zack Kaplan

deck: South African artist and writer, and creator of the South African superhero comic Kwezi.
description: Loyiso Mkize is a South African artist and founder of his own visual arts and communication company Loyiso Mkize Art (Pty) Ltd. He created its flagship South African superhero comic book, Kwezi. Prior to that, for seven years he was head illustrator of the Supa Strikas soccer comic book. He is also a painter.
name: Loyiso Mkize
